{"tid":2000660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果黃圈再壯大， 有冇機會影響商界？攻破功能組別？","createTime":"2020-05-04T04:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T04:47:07.000Z","uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9c4d9192fe39117227d90e2a8d459488359d2d","tid":2000660,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃金周，零售飲食都可以成億生意<br />\n商人會因為需要愛國同錢對抗？"},{"pid":"20b20781ae91a00d7d9f7216e509ac4c079b8986","tid":2000660,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"絕對有，但不是重點<br />\n<br />\n關於黃色經濟圈，我有d野想講：<br />\n<br />\n我想講翻其實黃色經濟圈最核心精神係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家幫襯黃店之外亦要記得先紅後藍：<br />\n<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b3330820a4358bd09fc095817ee7aa6b3e08a29","tid":2000660,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acee86aae2c98ed6c6dd542fc9058b1ebb5e4fb","tid":2000660,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6935686753e7a997aa4cf2f1612aa49dfa41c8aa","tid":2000660,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"推 對準目標"},{"pid":"70896d11af6a4cf609d83c6fe962ca5837915e67","tid":2000660,"uid":254684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe9c4d9192fe39117227d90e2a8d459488359d2d","tid":2000660,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃金周，零售飲食都可以成億生意<br />\n商人會因為需要愛國同錢對抗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"慶餘年"}]}